g":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1d608ac385dd5594962374884dce842d6d38d0","tid":1762310,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de8843ea30dfe0ceb07e16f7bfd5e3504fd7a1e4","tid":1762310,"uid":231864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T22:14:18.000Z","msg":"淨係洗牙可唔可以洗走黃牙？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"雖然有好多人都話要漂牙至得，但我自己嘅經驗嚟講就真係唔係囉，如果係遇到一個好牙醫，同你洗得夠乾淨、徹底，我以前日夜飲茶排黃+茶漬牙一樣會變得超級白，當然，如果個牙醫已經盡晒所有能力以洗牙方式去洗完都係黃嘅話，咁就係啲牙本身天生/隨著年紀而變黃啦，而非外在因素如飲食習慣，咁就先要迫住漂，當然就唔好畀啲hea洗牙醫呃到下下要漂先去到黃牙啦，如果我唔係以前遇到啲好牙醫洗牙洗到白返晒，都會畀啲差牙醫水到嘅！"},{"pid":"af8c4295911f2a12904393cb50df1442d8403c23","tid":1762310,"uid":283908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53c457cd18ae4680fa5cd0f0b054d6cf0fa8875d","tid":1762310,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b219454dffaddc5f8e4e5d76e5473b57da16bc6","tid":1762310,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d241d1121c1c4ccf51db45b77eb56c750a2cdc8","tid":1762310,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"hi 田田<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},{"pid":"b5de392997b2cf5ffa0fdd41101cbd1da8d8a8a8","tid":1762310,"uid":74162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39f873e8734a8d7adc7833fb05fc17e48a7bbad0","tid":1762310,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e56a13451acab0229ea532d5fda16e35ee24663e","tid":1762310,"uid":74162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit